# Ship only renv.lock into the image; the renv project infra (.Rprofile,
# renv/activate.R, renv/settings.json) is excluded so the container restores the
# lockfile the way the Dockerfile intends, without the renv autoloader interfering.
.Rprofile
renv/
dev
docs
tests
*.Rproj

